# ReadSync CODEOWNERS
# Format: <pattern>  <owner> [<owner2> ...]
# Owners are notified automatically for review when a PR touches matching paths.
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# ── Catch-all: core team reviews everything ───────────────────────────────────
*                                   @readsync/core

# ── Go source ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.go                                @readsync/core
go.mod                              @readsync/core
go.sum                              @readsync/core

# ── Adapters ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
internal/adapters/koreader/         @readsync/core
internal/adapters/moon/             @readsync/core
internal/adapters/calibre/          @readsync/core
internal/adapters/goodreads/        @readsync/core

# ── Core engine ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
internal/core/                      @readsync/core
internal/conflicts/                 @readsync/core
internal/resolver/                  @readsync/core
internal/outbox/                    @readsync/core
internal/db/                        @readsync/core

# ── Security-sensitive paths ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
internal/api/                       @readsync/core
internal/secrets/                   @readsync/core
tests/security/                     @readsync/core
SECURITY.md                         @readsync/core

# ── CI / GitHub automation ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.github/                            @readsync/core
.github/workflows/                  @readsync/core
.github/dependabot.yml              @readsync/core

# ── Installer & distribution ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
installer/                          @readsync/core
dist/                               @readsync/core

# ── Documentation ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
docs/                               @readsync/core
*.md                                @readsync/core
